text: Jessica Caroline Alexander (born 19 June 1999) is an English actress. She became well known for her roles in the BBC iPlayer series Get Even (2020) and in Disney's live-action musical fantasy movie The Little Mermaid (2023) as Vanessa. Jessica Caroline Alexander was born on 19 June 1999 in Westminster, London, England. She began acting at the age five.
